10#include "rtc_base/experiments/field_trial_list.h"
11
12namespace webrtc {
13
14FieldTrialListBase::FieldTrialListBase(std::string key)
15 : FieldTrialParameterInterface(key),
16 failed_(false),
17 parse_got_called_(false) {}
18
19bool FieldTrialListBase::Failed() const {
20 return failed_;
21}
22bool FieldTrialListBase::Used() const {
23 return parse_got_called_;
24}
25
26int FieldTrialListWrapper::Length() {
27 return GetList()->Size();
28}
29bool FieldTrialListWrapper::Failed() {
30 return GetList()->Failed();
31}
32bool FieldTrialListWrapper::Used() {
33 return GetList()->Used();
34}
35
36bool FieldTrialStructListBase::Parse(absl::optional<std::string> str_value) {
37 RTC_NOTREACHED();
38 return true;
39}
40
41int FieldTrialStructListBase::ValidateAndGetLength() {
42 int length = -1;
43 for (std::unique_ptr<FieldTrialListWrapper>& list : sub_lists_) {
44 if (list->Failed())
45 return -1;
46 else if (!list->Used())
47 continue;
48 else if (length == -1)
49 length = list->Length();
50 else if (length != list->Length())
51 return -1;
52 }
53
54 return length;
55}
56
57} // namespace webrtc
